    },
    {
        "verse_id": "92-93\u00bd",
        "text": " Now listen to me as I describe the eight principal urines which are enumerated in the system of Atreya. They are the urines of the ewe, she-goat, cow, she-buffalo, cowelephant, she-camel, mare and she-ass."
    },
    {
