efinitions\">Patanga</a> [<em><a data-gl=\"1\" href=\"/definition/patanga#ayurveda\" title=\"show pata\u1e45ga definitions\">pata\u1e45ga</a></em>], the <a data-gl=\"1\" href=\"/definition/tapaniya#ayurveda\" title=\"show Tapaniya definitions\">Tapaniya</a> [<em><a data-gl=\"1\" href=\"/definition/tapaniya#ayurveda\" title=\"show tapan\u012bya definitions\">tapan\u012bya</a></em>] and other good varieties of rice are cooling, sweet in taste and <a data-gl=\"1\" href=\"/definition/post#ayurveda\" title=\"show post definitions\">post</a>-digestion, slightly <a data-gl=\"1\" href=\"/definition/vata#ayurveda\" title=\"show Vata definitions\">Vata</a>-stimulant and form condensed and scanty stools",
