        "text": " The chital or spotted, deer, the elk or wapiti, the hangal or Kashmir deer, the mouse deer, the hog deer, the hare, the oorial or wild sheep, the roe deer, the mule deer, the Indian muntjak [muntjac?\u2014Muntiacus muntjak] or barking deer, the gazelle, the red deer, the black or Indian antelope, the Indian sam bhar, the black-tailed deer, the musk deer and the deerlet are the jangala animals."
