        "verse_id": "197",
        "text": " While falling from the sky it is influenced by the effects of the seasonal courses of the moon, the wind and, the sun. When is has fallen on the earth, it is affected by the qualities of the earth on which it falls viz. cold, heat, viscidity, dryness etc."
    },
